**Overview**

This dashboard offers a comprehensive view of alert events, showing data across key fields like severity, status, and confidence level. It features visualizations such as pie charts for event severity and confidence, a bar chart for status, a line graph for event trends over time, and tables listing the top 10 MITRE ATT&CK tactics, techniques, and compromised entities. 

[**Integrations Page**](/app/integrations/detail/microsoft_sentinel-0.1.0/overview)
